
########################################################################
Extract a pha2.fits and other analyzed results for grating observation
########################################################################

Scripts:
========

reprocess_warp_script
reprocess_main_script       #---- scripts to set environments

reprocess_warp_script.py
-------------------------

find a letg observation and add a pha2.fits and tg directory to /data/hrc/<inst>/analysis/

input:  /data/hrc/<inst>/secondary/* 

output: /data/hrc/<inst>/analysis/*pha2.fits
        /data/hrc/<inst>/analysis/tg/*

Environment: 
------------
setenv PYTHONPATH "/data/mta/Script/Python3.8/envs/ska3-shiny/lib/python3.8/site-packages:/data/mta/Script/Python3.8/lib/python3.8/site-packages/"

Inside of the python script, ciao environment is set:

source /soft/ciao/bin/ciao.csh -o








